{"id":78090,"type":4,"name":"Wizardry: Proving Grounds of the Mad Overlord","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e7/dd/78090_GtywY.jpg","summary":"《巫术：疯狂领主的试验场》是电子角色扮演游戏系列巫术的首款游戏。它由安德鲁·格林伯格和罗伯特·伍德黑德开发。诺曼·瑟尔特克在1980年建立Sir-Tech Software, Inc.，并在1980年波士顿电脑大会上展示了游戏测试版。游戏最终版于1981年发行。\r\n\r\n这是最早将龙与地下城式角色扮演游戏改写为电脑游玩的游戏之一，也是同类游戏中最早使用彩色画面的。这也是电子游戏史上首个回合团队制电子角色扮演游戏。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>巫术：疯狂领主的试验场</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/40315\">Sir-Tech</a> Software, Inc.</li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/40315\">Sir-Tech</a> Software, Inc.</li><li><span>别名: </span>Wizardry</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>巫术</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ウィザードリィ</li><li><span>平台: </span>SS</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>WSC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>GBC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>SFC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Sharp X1</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PCE</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC Booter</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC-98</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC-88</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>FC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>MSX</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Macintosh</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>FM-7</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Commodore 128</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Commodore 64</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Apple II</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>RPG</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>1981年</li><li><span>游戏设计师: </span>Andrew C. Greenberg, Robert Woodhead</li><li><span>原画: </span>Will McLean</li>","collection":{"collect":2,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"巫术","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":